						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone near the temple of Hanumān.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription engraved in characters of the <hi rend="bold">12th century A.D.,</hi> seems to record the death of <hi rend="bold">Asagara Kēta</hi> in a fight. <hi rend="bold">Goyda-Gauḍa</hi> the <hi rend="italic">prabhu</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Gaṇajūr</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Tantrapāḷa</hi> <hi rend="bold">Bammarasa</hi> are mentioned. </p>						

						</summary>
