<lb n="1"/>gaṇajūra prabhu goydagāvuḍanu samasta prajegaḷuviddu Asagara
<lb n="2"/>kēta <unclear>samastavu</unclear>pparavaṭṭada bīrana halavūra manneya bammarasa teṁ
<lb n="3" break="no"/>trapāḷa <unclear>hanasōge</unclear>yoḷu <unclear>gōṭa</unclear>keḷdalli vikramādityana <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
</p>

